---
import { images } from "../data/images";
---

<section class="about tint" id="about">
  <div class="sec-label reveal" style="grid-column: 1 / -1">
    <span class="num">04 / Studio</span>
    <h2>A quiet room<br>for <em>unquiet</em> bodies.</h2>
  </div>

  <p class="about-lede reveal">
    We believe the hour you give us should be the
    <em>best hour</em> of your day. Unhurried, precise, and honest
    about what your body actually needs.
  </p>

  <div class="about-body reveal">
    <p class="small">Founded 2026 · No. 17, Westbury Park</p>
    <p>
      Studio 17 is Emma's studio. Built into the side of her family home in
      Westbury Park, the room holds three reformers and one philosophy: pilates is
      about alignment, breathing and control, taught carefully.
    </p>
    <p>
      Classes are taught by Emma and Ruby. Both are classically trained, both
      are on first-name terms with every member, and both teach the same
      precise, unhurried way.
    </p>
    <p>
      New here? Begin with a <a href="/bookings" style="text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 4px;">Foundations class</a>
      or a <a href="/#contact" style="text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 4px;">private 1:1</a> to meet the
      equipment and find your starting line.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="principles reveal">
    <div>
      <div class="k">Class size</div>
      <div class="v">Three reformers, <em>always</em>.</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="k">Teachers</div>
      <div class="v">Emma &amp; <em>Ruby</em></div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="k">Method</div>
      <div class="v">Alignment · <em>breathing</em> · control</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="k">Pace</div>
      <div class="v">Deliberate, <em>slow</em>, strong</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-photo reveal">
    <div class="ph">
      <img src={images.studioInterior} alt="Studio 17 interior, reformers and natural light" />
      <span class="ph-label"><span class="sq"></span> Studio interior · wide</span>
      <span class="ph-tag">IMG · 02 · 16 : 7</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
